---
title: All-American Sriracha-Glazed Pork with Veggie Fries & Smokey Aioli
description: Herby, saucy and smokey - this American-style concoction is an explosion of colour and flavour! From the tasty sriracha-glazed pork to the rainbow fries and creamy slaw for crunch, every bite will knock your socks off!

